it.polimi.automata.io.ba.transformers

Class MetadataToBATransformer<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.automata.io.ba.transformers.MetadataToBATransformer<LABEL,STATE,TRANSITION>
  • Type Parameters:
    LABEL - is the type of the Label which is applied to the transitions of the Buchi Automaton which must implement the interface Label
    LABELFACTORY - is the factory which allows to create the labels of the transitions. It must implement the interface LabelFactory
    STATE - is the type of the State of the Buchi Automaton. It must extend the interface State
    STATEFACTORY - is the factory which is used to create the states of the Buchi Automaton. it must implement the interface StateFactory
    TRANSITION - is the type of the transitions of the automaton. It must implement the interface Transition
